{"tid":1296832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【長文】如果Be Water係咁樣  李小龍實恥笑我地","createTime":"2019-07-08T13:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T05:00:04.000Z","uid":37372,"like":179,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"2de0326783f31872adb3783fea2bb035f9a30ce3","tid":1296832,"uid":37372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:14:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Be water唔係解散水呀屌你老母</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>// Empty your mind, be formless, shapeless, like water. <br />\nYou put water into a cup, it becomes the cup.<br />\nYou put water into a teapot, it becomes the teapot. <br />\nWater can flow, or it can crash. <br />\nBe water my friend. //</em><br />\n- Bruce Lee <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/26jpiPaeL2LWo/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F26jpiPaeL2LWo%2Fgiphy.gif&h=8bc41e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>◆ Be Water： 點樣 &quot;Water&quot; 固然重要 更重要係個 &quot;Be&quot; ！</strong></span> <br />\n李小龍講嘅 &quot;Be Water My Friend&quot;，原典其實出自《孫子兵法 虛實篇》： 「夫兵形象水，水之形，避高而趨下：兵之形，避實而擊虛；水因地而制流，兵因敵而制勝。故兵無常勢，水無常形；能因敵變化而取勝，謂之神。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係作戰時應該 <span style=\"color: red;\">靈活變通 不拘於形 避實擊虛 因敵制勝</span><br />\n所以Be Water，係強調作戰時要Be Water，你無打算作戰，無諗住贏，你Be乜都無所謂喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">◆ When water is in a CHAMBER, it should become the fucking CHAMBER!</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWater can flow, or it can crash. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地由6月9日至7月1日咁長時間，一直都flow緊黎保存實力，令到黑警疲態盡現；<br />\n到7月1日，我地佔領住議會，將會係整場運動中我地同政府bargain既最重要籌碼&mdash;<br />\n係呢個時候，當呢場運動經過長久既拉鋸，終於flow into the right position，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地係未要一野crash落去呢？</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你，點知唔係，反而係散水！當入左立法會果班義士聽到出面愈黎愈少人，你知唔知佢地幾絕望？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Water that can only flow but not crash is no water but air!</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">◆ 如果不受傷不被捕係終極目標既 咁BE AT HOME算啦</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>1）不受傷不被捕係為左咩野？</strong><br />\n<br />\n如果 <strong>#不受傷不被捕</strong> 就係終極目標，咁如果大家從來都唔出黎抗爭，未一定唔會受傷同被捕囉！<span style=\"color: red;\">Don't be Water, just be at home.</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以，不受傷不被捕並唔係天條，而只係一個保留實力既方法。不受傷不被捕，係為左盡量減少casualties既同時進行騷擾作戰。<strong>#盡量以低成本換高戰果 #並為決戰做準備</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2）你有冇見過李小龍be water，係一見對面出拳氣勢強就即刻逃走避戰？</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n李小龍體格天生比歐洲人或者黑人弱小，佢會避開敵人既攻擊，但絕對唔會逃走避戰。當佢係避開對手攻擊既過程中，睇到對手露出破綻，就係佢主動出撃既時候。<br />\n<br />\n我好希望下次再有呢個破綻出現既時候，大家唔好再用Be Water做藉口叫人散水，大家咁做只會係<span style=\"color: red;\">陷左最前線肯搏殺既兄弟於死地。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝大家。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqpj7H2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmqpj7H2.gif&h=de954cf5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"484c38b0fc35c725d54121576a052b2ca31a1c95","tid":1296832,"uid":273176,"like":52,"dislike":3,"score":49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:16:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢一定笑唔出<br />\n連登次次一完活動都話Be water 散水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LwTAt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LwTAt.gif&h=31f9de48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f085e1ccb06cf5b57a4f264d6c94b3b6c0675d6","tid":1296832,"uid":172677,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:17:18.000Z","msg":"四字總結 融會貫通"},{"pid":"138d965372930be83a3a68c4c1a02de8d6e9e2d0","tid":1296832,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:17:34.000Z","msg":"「運動末來發展」我想分享少少意見同建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295758\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295758</a>"},{"pid":"f63a9b4b6775531fee30b4c4bdd076617c868718","tid":1296832,"uid":33736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"e3c59bc5f57576a803a779450f09deb44df6e929","tid":1296832,"uid":226640,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:26:50.000Z","msg":"無㗎喎 一有人大嗌有狗就散一堆 <br />\n搞到留係度既人仲驚 又散一堆"},{"pid":"853701a81430ddcaa41971a7043b67955d99666e","tid":1296832,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:29:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92de03a1796217b357070c110b3833eb1b82ba73","tid":1296832,"uid":743,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"呢啲長文冇人睇架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9049afa448a620603eac140f7cf3203cb162e2cf","tid":1296832,"uid":32221,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:37:24.000Z","msg":"關鍵係你仲係抱住打不還手既信條你係唔會有可能可以擋到full gear狗衝，咁唔適當散水又可以點呢？就佔立法會果晚計，台灣太陽花班人都話此狗不同彼台警，佢地都話要撤"},{"pid":"60acec8e0214794cef4589d4f06d6d47a27cb3dd","tid":1296832,"uid":42456,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"不受傷不被捕be water呢幾句真係難聽過粗口<br />\n猶其是後面話有狗就散嗰班真係唔好叫同路人<br />\n同泛民一樣都係會出賣前線"},{"pid":"40f807d31cac716882d3e2ed39e247288681f423","tid":1296832,"uid":219533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:40:23.000Z","msg":"冇還手準備<br />\n真係at home算啦"},{"pid":"ff7ef5e6fb20c1552ddf25db234e8f7571f6899a","tid":1296832,"uid":273176,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9049afa448a620603eac140f7cf3203cb162e2cf","tid":1296832,"uid":