1296832,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:25:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0b78a49b50f6d2b6d5a9d758918a174b47fde56","tid":1296832,"uid":273176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4531207af4effe786d6ba116b90c0d5725ce1d00","tid":1296832,"uid":276293,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:22:28.000Z","msg":"俾人圍時散水 = 避開<br />\n咁難明?<br />\n<br />\n你叫人唔好散即係硬食一拳"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:31:59.000Z","msg":"依家未比人圍 連登已經叫人Be water <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n琴晚走緊 都比人屌冇be water <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560e9ff329919a4f6149d071660bf2e1a9e8f74d","tid":1296832,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:41:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcbbdefc651b6777eff32f992ca77be314a9b083","tid":1296832,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:41:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"666ac6a51f85f9fd5d772750cbb6072f87f419f5","tid":1296832,"uid":31609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3938336efc41757433f22994f9cf83c91184f98","tid":1296832,"uid":221699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:00:56.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n啱啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但和理非啱先升做少少勇武<br />\n我諗要啲時間比佢地去理解同實行呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7f7cf71e21dd5a701dfc540f9a47683d467a4e","tid":1296832,"uid":176405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:09:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cf24980e5e65c8ff82e41dd4aa18ff6741842e9","tid":1296832,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:13:22.000Z","msg":"有小小建議 哨兵通知現場有狗既時候可以冷靜d 除非真係好危急 用普通通知既語氣 否則會造成驚慌 好多細路或新手真係唔識判形勢雞飛狗走"},{"pid":"a4e3b8f99662609d61b740f3ad45c738082658e9","tid":1296832,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:19:36.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181949e1e4b8646072f664d912e426774ce201ea","tid":1296832,"uid":264536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:52:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"549da39dc9897a04fcd13f095915a6840cfab890","tid":1296832,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:23:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e8fa9858bb745397d8ba706e59f1e8ea9a6737a","tid":1296832,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2de0326783f31872adb3783fea2bb035f9a30ce3","tid":1296832,"uid":37372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:14:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Be water唔係解散水呀屌你老母</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>// Empty your mind, be formless, shapeless, like water. <br />\nYou put water into a cup, it becomes the cup.<br />\nYou put water into a teapot, it becomes the teapot. <br />\nWater can flow, or it can crash. <br />\nBe water my friend. //</em><br />\n- Bruce Lee <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/26jpiPaeL2LWo/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F26jpiPaeL2LWo%2Fgiphy.gif&h=8bc41e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>◆ Be Water： 點樣 &quot;Water&quot; 固然重要 更重要係個 &quot;Be&quot; ！</strong></span> <br />\n李小龍講嘅 &quot;Be Water My Friend&quot;，原典其實出自《孫子兵法 虛實篇》： 「夫兵形象水，水之形，避高而趨下：兵之形，避實而擊虛；水因地而制流，兵因敵而制勝。故兵無常勢，水無常形；能因敵變化而取勝，謂之神。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係作戰時應該 <span style=\"color: red;\">靈活變通 不拘於形 避實擊虛 因敵制勝</span><br />\n所以Be Water，係強調作戰時要Be Water，你無打算作戰，無諗住贏，你Be乜都無所謂喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">◆ When water is in a CHAMBER, it should become the fucking CHAMBER!</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWater can flow, or it can crash. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地由6月9日至7月1日咁長時間，一直都flow緊黎保存實力，令到黑警疲態盡現；<br />\n到7月1日，我地佔領住議會，將會係整場運動中我地同政府bargain既最重要籌碼&mdash;<br />\n係呢個時候，當呢場運動經過長久既拉鋸，終於flow into the right position，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地係未要一野crash落去呢？</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你，點知唔係，反而係散水！當入左立法會果班義士聽到出面愈黎愈少人，你知唔知佢地幾絕望？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Water that can only flow but not crash is no water but air!</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">◆ 如果不受傷不被捕係終極目標既 咁BE AT HOME算啦</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>1）不受傷不被捕係為左咩野？</strong><br />\n<br />\n如果 <strong>#不受傷不被捕</strong> 就係終極目標，咁如果大家從來都唔出黎抗爭，未一定唔會受傷同被捕囉！<span style=\"color: red;\">Don't be Water, just be at home.</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以，不受傷不被捕並唔係天條，而只係一個保留實力既方法。不受傷不被捕，係為左盡量減少casualties既同時進行騷擾作戰。<strong>#盡量以低成本換高戰果 #並為決戰做準備</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2）你有冇見過李小龍be water，係一見對面出拳氣勢強就即刻逃走避戰？</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n李小龍體格天生比歐洲人或者黑人弱小，佢會避開敵人既攻擊，但絕對唔會逃走避戰。當佢係避開對手攻擊既過程中，睇到對手露出破綻，就係佢主動出撃既時候。<br />\n<br />\n我好希望下次再有呢個破綻出現既時候，大家唔好再用Be Water做藉口叫人散水，大家咁做只會係<span style=\"color: red;\">陷左最前線肯搏殺既兄弟於死地。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝大家。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqpj7H2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmqpj7H2.gif&h=de954cf5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:08:42.000Z","msg":"高質post冇人睇<br />\n<br />\n次次大家佔領完第日就繼續返學返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da3ceaae7e7c1159cc12f94fac961386b94e487","tid":1296832,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T09:27:19.000Z","msg":"BE SANDBAG<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/MuDY69D.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMuDY69D.gif&h=b3def13b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28e25db55fa98aedca7d34e02feb9985a3c001e0","tid":1296832,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T09:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde5fe9b736b7331af053087aab748bf272b09dc","tid":1296832,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"484c38b0fc35c725d54121576a052b2ca31a1c95","tid":1296832,"uid":273176,"like":52,"dislike":3,"score":49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:16:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢一定笑唔出<br />\n連登次次一完活動都話Be water 散水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LwTAt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LwTAt.gif&h=31f9de48&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:06:47.000Z","msg":"呢幅圖好唔老禮"},{"pid":"ef026e4723695799e66af6ed198290fb82f498fa","tid":1296832,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"又話轉場元朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a605ed741b8483af310e0e9aed43ad531e8220","tid":1296832,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"484c38b0fc35c725d54121576a052b2ca31a1c95","tid":1296832,"uid":273176,"like":52,"dislike":3,"score":49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:16:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢一定笑唔出<br />\n連登次次一完活動都話Be water 散水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LwTAt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LwTAt.gif&h=31f9de48&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:09:07.000Z","msg":"係咁想笑"},{"pid":"20246d3a921748cfe30b00fdbb3ccd46b498792f","tid":1296832,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:09:48.000Z","msg":"佢地就係想激撚醒李小龍"},{"pid":"e1bd0cb27774683e99f8144fca1493066121a638","tid":1296832,"uid":8600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:14:47.000Z","msg":"經過今日更加知道現場冇呢個概念<br />\n次次整完防線就等對面組隊黎掃場<br />\n明明係冇野需要守，唔單只上水同旺角，所有冇戰略目的既地點都唔應該守，除非有打算勇武<br />\n對面經過上次海濱已經唔會比機會你走，除非好似71咁多人<br />\n我想講1212都只係夠多人對峙果陣用<br />\n下次再係類似情況請立刻轉移陣地，示威者機動性係高好多，而且對面行動係要等命令"},{"pid":"04ebda4ad51600fab499b660a7030ea25f404c8e","tid":1296832,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:16:22.000Z","msg":"每次咁樣蝕一堆人比人拉真係好唔抵<br />\n鐘意屌我冷氣軍師既隨便"},{"pid":"50ac7ed3e09a9f8ecf8f119a8be8f956afa95ad1","tid":1296832,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:17:40.000Z","msg":"吓點樣上到熱門㗎<br />\n四日前嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我上極都上唔到嘅"},{"pid":"1eb12d7fefb181a3974937b12a1940c40cdc90a2","tid":1296832,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7031908d35df99fce0dcc18db5ec38f4f4251485","tid":1296832,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:21:47.000Z","msg":"同埋如果示威者係上水走黎走去啲走私撚已經唔洗開鋪<br />\n自己諗下係咪下下都要中世紀打必輸陣地戰<br />\n仲有叫咪非法集結已經要決定下一步，唔係等人清"},{"pid":"383a2be0381a2e284aae9200e424abdc00812ddb","tid":1296832,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50ac7ed3e09a9f8ecf8f119a8be8f956afa95ad1","tid":1296832,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:17:40.000Z","msg":"吓點樣上到熱門㗎<br />\n四日前嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我上極都上唔到嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:24:31.000Z","msg":"因為真係好撚嬲<br />\n上次旺角啲狗已經擺明圍鳩你都仲黎多次<br />\n唔好再覺得宜家佢地會慢慢黎守例<br />\n林奠都講到明已經押哂落啲狗道一定會攬<br />\n你唔反擊佢地只係等齊人黎趕羊<br />\n唔係想分化<br />\n只係想出去既其他人諗清楚目的同做下風險評估"},{"pid":"920c38a1b82f28b0a5bb29ddeeafa34c5fb737df","tid":1296832,"uid":63808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"[學術分享]今日教大家點樣整套索捉畜生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1310665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1310665</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"91ba7fb8b9d688ed7054f5981c58abfae31a2343","tid":1296832,"uid":63808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f085e1ccb06cf5b57a4f264d6c94b3b6c0675d6","tid":1296832,"uid":172677,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:17:18.000Z","msg":"四字總結 融會貫通"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:45:57.000Z","msg":"[求屌醒!]我今日唔會去上水！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1310838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1310838</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b7f69e5f5e0fa35b414b18ba11a6e0fc8f6b10f","tid":1296832,"uid":130488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:50:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5e4dc73763a2d01ea58c37bbf0e7642a8d007d98","tid":1296832,"uid":266938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:13:01.000Z","msg":"推"}]}